headline: Banking at the Bottom of the World: Diebold Nixdorf ATMs Now Serving Antarctica
summary: Diebold Nixdorf (NYSE: DBD), a world leader in transforming the way people bank and shop, announces the successful installation of two DN Series® ATMs at the U.S. National Science Foundation (NSF) McMurdo Station, Antarctica. Operated by Wells Fargo, the new cash dispensers replace the previously installed units, further enhancing accessibility to cash in one of the world's most remote locations.
